name: The Lost Sandal - (Holographic Version)
description:
The Lost Sandal - (Holographic Version)

The long lost sandal that was lost during Friday prayers is now found. It's in the metaverse, floating around. If you ever have lost one sandal in your life, get them back now. 

This is a holographic video. use HoloPrism (holographic viewfinder) to get the best vision of this sandal.
